OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fwith 'brazen' shoplifters  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A convenience store owner says he      
OL,6, witnesses up to nine shoplifting       
OL,7, incidents a day, with criminals who are
OL,8, "more brazen and aggressive".          
OL,10,FBenedict Selvaratnam says it is because
OL,11,Fshoplifters know they are not a police 
OL,12,Fpriority.                              
OL,14,FHis situation is being echoed in small 
OL,15,Fshops across the UK, according to the  
OL,16,FFederation of Independent Retailers.   
OL,18,FThe group, which represents 10,000     
OL,19,Fshopkeepers, is calling for government 
OL,20,Fhelp to tackle the problem.            
